tool_description: The logoraisr VectorTracing API converts jpeg and png to svg, by tracing the pixels to vectors.
name: logoraisr VectorTracing
title: logoraisr VectorTracing

api_list.name: Get download url for result
api_list.description: Get the result image url from the processed image, by passing the `result_file_id` as path parameter in the request url. You get the `result_file_id` as response after creating a project.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://logoraisr-vectortracing.p.rapidapi.com/rest-v1/results/e4eb301dbeaf495db60e787285b98100/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "logoraisr-vectortracing.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
